(2. Evaluation Against the Project Aim) Tj
ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 28.00 359.00 Tm 13 TL
(The overall aim of the project was to design, develop, and evaluate a secure desktop-based apartment) Tj
T*
(management system using Python Tkinter and MySQL. This aim has been achieved to a strong academic) Tj
T*
(standard. The completed application provides a working multi-user solution that supports apartment) Tj
T*
(administration, tenant management, maintenance processing, billing operations, reporting, and tenant) Tj
T*
(self-service functionality.) Tj
ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 28.00 288.00 Tm 13 TL
(The final system demonstrates that the team moved beyond analysis and design into a functioning software) Tj
T*
(product with persistent data storage, clear business rules, and role-specific workflows. As a result,) Tj
T*
(the project is suitable for both technical discussion and live demonstration.) Tj
